*Doctor teaching a child how to use an inhaler*

Q:"What is an inhaler?"
Q:"Why do I need to use an inhaler?"
Q:"When should I use it?"
Q:"Why is it bitter? I don't like it"
Q:"Will it explode?"
Q:"Can I give it to my friends?"


*Doctor teaching a child about their insulin shots*
Q:"Why do I need to get the shots?"
Q:"It hurts, Can I not do it?"
Q:"Why can't I have chocolate?"
Q:"I feel good, so I don't need the shots?"
Q:"When can I stop?"
